+ Class Methods

++ Public

* Solar_Filter::alnum() -- Returns only alphanumeric characters within a value.

* Solar_Filter::alpha() -- Returns only alphabetic characters within a value.

* Solar_Filter::blank() -- Returns only whitespace characters within a value.

* Solar_Filter::callback() -- Uses a callback to filter a value.

* Solar_Filter::cast() -- Uses [[php settype()]] to cast a value as a PHP variable type.

* Solar_Filter::formatDate() -- Forces a value to a date format using [[php date()]].

* Solar_Filter::formatTime() -- Forces a value to a time format using [[php date()]].

* Solar_Filter::formatTimestamp() -- Forces a value to a timestamp format using [[php date()]].

* Solar_Filter::multiple() -- Applies multiple filters to a value.

* Solar_Filter::numeric() -- Returns only numbers within a value.

* Solar_Filter::pregReplace() -- Applies a [[php preg_replace()]] filter.

* Solar_Filter::strReplace() -- Applies a [[php str_replace()]] filter.

* Solar_Filter::stripAlnum() -- Strips alphanumeric characters from a value.

* Solar_Filter::stripAlpha() -- Strips alphabetic characters from a value.

* Solar_Filter::stripBlank() -- Strips all whitespace from a value.

* Solar_Filter::stripNumeric() -- Strips all numbers from a value.

* Solar_Filter::stripWord() -- Strips word characters from a value.

* Solar_Filter::trim() -- Trims characters from the beginning and end of a value.

* Solar_Filter::word() -- Returns only word characters within a value.

